ce:list-item.ce:para:
Determine the total number of cycles N, set
n = 1
;

Determine the quantity M of each EV type and input the initial parameters, set
m = 1
;

The driving mileage and energy consumption per 100 km of the 
                                    m
                                 th EV are randomly selected;

Set
m = m + 1
to judge whether m is equal to M. If so, go to (9). If not, go to (3);

Set
n = n + 1
to judge whether n is equal to N. If so, go to (10). If not, go to (2);

Allocate the number of cycles 
                                    n
                                  to the multi-core CPU, and each core is allocated about 8/N cycles to establish parallel tasks;
